title: TASK_WARP_PED_INTO_VEHICLE
content:
0x65D4A35D// TaskWarpPedIntoVehicle
void TASK_WARP_PED_INTO_VEHICLE(Ped ped, Vehicle vehicle, int seatIndex);Parameters:ped: The Ped to be warped into the vehicle.vehicle: The target vehicle into which the ped will be warped.seatIndex: See eSeatPosition declared in IS_VEHICLE_SEAT_FREE.NativeDB Introduced: v323Warp a ped into a vehicle.
Note: It's better to use TASK_ENTER_VEHICLE with the flag "warp" flag instead of this native.This is the server-side RPC native equivalent of the client native TASK_WARP_PED_INTO_VEHICLE.
